# Test consistency of outputs

This test mixes all existing type structures, with slightly cursed field,
constructor and ident names.

```catala-metadata
declaration enumeration Tenûm:
  -- Ĉ content boolean
  -- Ĉ2 content integer

declaration structure Tstrûc:
  data f_ê content list of Tenûm
  data f_1 content (date, duration, duration, duration)
  data f_ôô content (optional of Period, optional of Period)
  data f_ûû content list of (decimal, money)
```


```catala
#[test]
declaration scope Ŝ:
  output ô content Tstrûc

scope Ŝ:
  definition ô equals
    Tstrûc {
      -- f_ê : [Ĉ content true; Ĉ content false; Ĉ2 content -1000000]
      -- f_1 : (|0000-01-01|, 0 day, 1 year, 2 year + 1 month + 2 day)
      -- f_ôô : (Absent, Present content Period { -- begin: |2001-01-01| -- end: |2001-07-01| })
      -- f_ûû : [(0.0, $0); (-1000.0, -$1000); (1000.000001, $1000.01); (-0.0000001, -$0)]
}
```
